n newsletter. There are at least 25 links of amazing related stuff to go and dig into, from recipes to beautiful planet-friendly things to buy.”\n      <div class=\"brimm-testimonial-footer\">\n        <span class=\"brimm-testimonial-author\">— Matt, Marketing Strategist</span>\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0847/6891/5798/files/matt-testimonials.webp?v=1750092551\" alt=\"Matt\" class=\"brimm-testimonial-headshot\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"brimm-testimonial\">\n      “Reading it felt like I’d stumbled across an interesting community of people sharing unknown gems.”\n      <div class=\"brimm-testimonial-footer\">\n        <span class=\"brimm-testimonial-author\">— Tiff, Journalist and Author</span>\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0847/6891/5798/files/tiff-testimonials.webp?v=1750092551\" alt=\"Tiff\" class=\"brimm-testimonial-headshot\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"brimm-testimonial\">\n      “I love the breadth of links they feature. From mind-expanding long-reads, to the latest restaurants or a great new fashion brand.”\n      <div class=\"brimm-testimonial-footer\">\n        <span class=\"brimm-testimonial-author\">— Shiraz, Playlist Maker</span>\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0847/6891/5798/files/shiraz-testimonials.webp?v=1750182257\" alt=\"User icon\" class=\"brimm-testimonial-headshot\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
